ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of ROBERT PHILPOTT of Summerside, Prince Edward Island, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum for Human Rights, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, effective June 22, 2019, in the place of Lindy Ledohowski, whose term has expired.
